%F A105064 From _G. C. Greubel_, Mar 12 2023: (Start)
%F A105064 T(n, k) = T(n, k-1) + (k+1)*n!, T(n, 0) = 1.
%F A105064 T(n, n-1) = (1/2)*((n^2 + n - 2)*n! + 2).
